name: Supreme Swarovski Box Logo Hooded Sweatshirt
description: In April of 1994, Supreme New York first opened their doors in downtown Manhattan. April 2019 marks 25 years since, and in honor of that, Supreme released a special edition of their iconic box logo hooded sweatshirt. Featuring a box logo made of Swarovski Crystals, the hooded sweatshirts released in four iconic colorways; red on grey, black on black, red on navy, and red on red.

name: LEGO Star Wars Cloud City Set 10123
description: 10123 Cloud City was a 698 piece Star Wars exclusive set with 7 minifigs released in 2003. It is based on the film Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back

name: LEGO Green Grocer Set 10185
description: Expand your LEGO neighborhood or start a new one with the Green Grocer! Designed in a modular style, this colorful and lively building features a grocery store and classic apartments that can be built, rebuilt and rearranged to suit your own LEGO town.

name: LEGO Star Wars Super Star Destroyer Set 10221
description: The LEGO Star Wars Super Star Destroyer Set 10221 is a 3,152 piece model of the deadly battleship seen in the original Star Wars Trilogy. The set measures nearly 50 inches in length once completed, and features a removable center section that reveals the ship's command center. With the LEGO Star Wars Super Star Destroyer Set 10221 you will also receive five LEGO Star Wars Minifigures: Darth Vader, Admiral Piett, Dengar, Bossk, and IG-88.

name: LEGO Star Wars Death Star II 10143
description: 10143 Death Star II was a 3,441 piece Star Wars set released in 2005.

name: LEGO Technic Porsche 911 GT3 RS Set 42056
description: Experience the iconic Porsche 911 GT3 RS with this authentic LEGO Technic replica. Inside the box you'll discover a special collector's book chronicling the history of LEGO Technic and Porsche GT cars, together with 4 original-design rims bearing the RS emblem. The sets of elements are boxed, and the building sequence gives an insight into the real-life vehicle's assembly process.

name: NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3090 Founders Edition Graphics Card
description: The GeForce RTX 3090 Founders Edition Graphics Card is a big ferocious GPU (BFGPU) with TITAN class performance, making it one of the best GPUs available on the market. The GeForce RTX 3090 Founders Edition Graphics Card is powered by NVIDIA's 2nd generation RTX architecture (Ampere) — doubling down on ray tracing and AI performance with enhanced Ray Tracing Cores, Tensor Cores, and streaming multiprocessors. The GPU also features a staggering 24 GB of G6X memory, delivering the ultimate gaming and content creation experience.

name: NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3080 Founders Edition Graphics Card
description: Step up your graphics with the RTX 3080 Founders Edition. The NVIDIA-made RTX 3080 Founders Edition is advanced in its features, including a dual-fan system, 10GB of RAM, and boost clock speeds of 1.71 GHz.

name: Charizard 1999 Pokémon TCG
description: The Charizard Holo Base Set 1st Edition is the most iconic and valuable card in the hobby. Charizard is one of two Fire Type Pokémon offered in the Base Set Holos, the other being Ninetales. Accompanied by Blastoise and Venusaur, Charizard is one of the final stage evolutions of the original three starter Pokémon.
